":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/94/s302/a/6"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–94, § 302(a)(6)","children":[],"tail":", added par. (8). Former par. (8) redesignated (11)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Pars. (9), (10). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/94/s302/a/7"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–94, § 302(a)(7)","children":[],"tail":", added pars. (9) and (10). Former par. (9) redesignated (12)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Pars. (11), (12). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/94/s302/a/3"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–94, § 302(a)(3)","children":[],"tail":", redesignated pars. (8) and (9) as (11) and (12), respectively."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2009—Par. (1). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/90/s4/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–90, § 4(1)","children":[],"tail":", struck out “Morris K. Udall Scholarship and Excellence in National Environmental Policy” before “Foundation”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Pars. (5), (9). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/90/s4/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–90, § 4(2)","children":[],"tail":", (3), substituted “and Stewart L. Udall” for “Scholarship and Excellence in National Environmental Policy”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1998—Pars. (4), (5). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/156/s2/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 105–156, § 2(1)","children":[],"tail":", (2), added par. (4) and redesignated former par. (4) as (5). Former par. (5) redesignated (9)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Par. (6). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/244"},"text":"Pub. L. 105–244","children":[],"tail":", which directed the substitution of “section 1001” for “section 1141(a)” in par. (6), could not be executed because “section 1141(a)” did not appear in text."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/156/s2/3"},